{"tid":1557401,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要 軍心] 各位手足聽到音樂舉起呢個手勢","createTime":"2019-09-10T05:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T16:01:41.000Z","uid":80905,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ad0623d5da0127afc300e133f1035aaee3cfc8","tid":1557401,"uid":80905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"[太長唔睇] <br />\n響起願榮光歸香港 舉hunger game 手勢<br />\n<br />\n正評舉 負評不舉<br />\n---------<br />\n小弟係9.9集會途中<br />\n行到中銀對出有位full suit + 豬咀既手足<br />\n佢開大聲公請在場香港人高舉hunger game手勢<br />\n然後一齊唱願榮光歸香港 <br />\n最後將高舉手勢果隻手放係心口<br />\n寓意將呢隻歌送比死去既同伴<br />\n發誓唔會屈服係呢個極權底下 <br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n果一刻 我覺得我同在場既全部香港人connected <br />\n我地有自己奮鬥既歌 <br />\n有一個代表我地理念既手勢<br />\n對振奮軍心 團結香港人有好大幫助<br />\n<br />\n我搵過幾個相關討論既post<br />\n有人話好中二 <br />\n有人話驚比紅媒影到話nazi<br />\n有人話好柒 有人話弱智手勢<br />\n<br />\n小弟覺得講黎都多鳩餘<br />\n當時討論嗌時代革命咪一樣又係好多人唔buy<br />\n<br />\n你驚比紅媒影到屈係nazi就仲好笑<br />\n紅媒受眾就係藍絲 佢地連你透啖氣都想斬你架啦<br />\n<br />\n呢個手勢其實當年泰國人對抗軍政府果陣都有用黎做無聲抗議<br />\n加上hunger game套戲全球大熱 無人唔知呢個手勢既意思啦<br />\n<br />\n你覺得好中二唔想舉 你都on99<br />\n而加係對抗極權 係打仗 <br />\n你平時係動漫先見到既情節而加發生係我地既香港到<br />\n呢件事本身就好中二架啦<br />\n<br />\n你不舉你既事<br />\n我就係夢境每次聽到音樂都舉到音樂完然後將手放係心口<br />\n<br />\n最後跪求認同既手足幫手做文宣! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xuu9VM2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxuu9VM2.jpg&h=98a2131e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8S7Hr3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8S7Hr3.jpg&h=e9c9983e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QMJuVM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQMJuVM4.jpg&h=da6a811e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5uXjyyL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5uXjyyL.jpg&h=7d72bfa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxXSTyM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxXSTyM.jpg&h=8a01228d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港!!<br />\n時代革命!!"},{"pid":"31fb4654a1e67ebb790e36b8938d0949bd429f62","tid":1557401,"uid":303911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"P 仔 can't push"},{"pid":"76a526c9bb80458faa8e9bfaabe9560010ff9052","tid":1557401,"uid":80905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:56:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee4473378eb97965d29ce3b240c3fa267f85b14c","tid":1557401,"uid":80905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:56:31.000Z","msg":"推x2"},{"pid":"92d054fa3f2c0de7c562e951379241f0573ed9d8","tid":1557401,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:58:01.000Z","msg":"右邊係放心臟定左手"},{"pid":"f942afb8ec0298e137655e864cb264cfcae32711","tid":1557401,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T05:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有得諗"},{"pid":"2dd2041caee4d3d0d5bb94d15ae361a9f121e59b","tid":1557401,"uid":37922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:01:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a69eefc7e6eaab3d9787808744fceb47c5bf8e3f","tid":1557401,"uid":98313,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:03:37.000Z","msg":"放係隻眼到"},{"pid":"96b46de1be327a9f292b2b1999264bb88a6c0059","tid":1557401,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:06:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0f5bc425e12ede0b7db43d67e0a6645622fcdf1","tid":1557401,"uid":260695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:08:04.000Z","msg":"推"},